up.

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:47.099
But it'll sure come in handy, because this
will inevitably move over time.

00:02:47.099 --> 00:02:50.970
Now, the final finish on the floor is gonna
be paint.

00:02:50.970 --> 00:02:55.530
I'm gonna paint the floors, so that's why
it didn't bother me to have to come in and

00:02:55.530 --> 00:03:00.420
